Privacy Policy for ArtWorks

This privacy policy describes how ArtWorks (the "app") collects, uses, and discloses your personal information when you use the app.

What information do we collect?

The app does not collect any personal information from you or your device. The app only accesses your device's camera and photo library to allow you to create and edit artworks using the app's features. The app does not store, transmit, or share any of the images or data that you process with the app.

How do we use your information?

The app does not use your information for any purpose, as it does not collect any information from you or your device.

How do we protect your information?

The app does not need to protect your information, as it does not collect any information from you or your device. However, the app uses encryption and security measures to prevent unauthorized access to the app's code and functionality.

Do we disclose any information to third parties?

The app does not disclose any information to third parties, as it does not collect any information from you or your device.

Changes to our privacy policy

We may update our privacy policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new privacy policy on this page. You are advised to review this privacy policy periodically for any changes.

Contact us

If you have any questions or suggestions about our privacy policy, please contact us at mahdidvb72@gmail.com.
